# ============================================================================
# MK OS — Self-Modifications Log
# ============================================================================
# This file records ALL changes MK makes to its own knowledge base.
# Every modification is logged with timestamp, type, and before/after state.
# User can review, approve, or revert any modification.
#
# Format: # timestamp | type
#         # Description: what was changed
#         # Before: previous state
#         new_state_entry
#
# Types: add_fact, add_rule, disable_rule, merge, correction, proposal, revert
#
# SAFETY: MK never modifies this file without creating a log entry.
#         All changes are reversible.
# ============================================================================
